{
  "stem": "12768.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So the family were always together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And that first start breaking up when everybody, my older brothers and my sister got married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And, and my aunt and uncle's children also got married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it kind of fizzled out, like one say, because then you get your own family unit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And that was what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But we lived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We went to the synagogue in Copenhagen, and, and-- you have to excuse me-- and so on the big holidays because it was quite a ride to, to get in there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And of course, we had-- it wasn't so much that you just came to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "That was the part that you always looked at, you know, and so that you had to take the train [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "You could always buy the ticket the day before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And therefore, you didn't use money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "But that was what you had to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I remember the big holidays-- holiday was standing from early morning till late night, you know, in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And then we went home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And then my father asked us to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "We cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And we said, no, it takes so long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And it was very hard, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "But at that time, we had a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "His name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "He was of German extraction, you know, and asked to come to Denmark to become a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "But he had a funny thing that he really didn't try to learn Danish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And so he was very hard to understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And I had my bar mitzvah with him, or confirmation-- whatever you said in those days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And he was, he was almost impossible.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
